### Manual Verification

1. `docker-compose up` ‚Üí EventLens UI at `http://localhost:9090`
2. `java -jar eventlens.jar --help` ‚Äî all subcommands displayed
3. Search aggregate ‚Üí timeline ‚Üí state viewer ‚Üí diff highlighting
4. Live stream: insert event in PG ‚Üí appears in WebSocket panel
5. Bisect CLI: `bisect ACC-001 --where "balance < 0"` ‚Üí correct event found
6. `--classpath /path/to/reducers.jar` ‚Üí custom reducer loaded and used
